4. Write a program in Python using generators to reverse the string.
Input String = “Consultadd Training”



Ans:

input_string = "Consultadd Training"

def rev_str(my_str):
    length = len(my_str)
    for i in range(length - 1, -1, -1):
        yield my_str[i]


reverse_str = ""
for i in rev_str(input_string):
    reverse_str += i


print(reverse_str)



